    "This has been a long-standing challenge in TDA (further discussed in Sect. 3.3), but topological layers are now becoming compatible with deep learning and end-to-end training schemes.",
    "We reiterate that though the benefits of using TDA (more specifically, persistent homology) and deep learning together have demonstrated success, there are still some theoretical and computational challenges in the application of TDA to data.",
    "We discuss these issues at length in Sect. 4.2.",
    "In the rest of this section, we investigate TDA for deep learning from lenses of different magnifications and perspectives, as shown in Fig. 4.",
    "In particular, we explore the use of persistent homology in various different ways."
